    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749050/extras/96e17b0fcd87ee8c6d7a9cc27d738358.poster.avif?t=1653674457\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749050/extras/96e17b0fcd87ee8c6d7a9cc27d738358.webm?t=1653674457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1749050/extras/96e17b0fcd87ee8c6d7a9cc27d738358.mp4?t=1653674457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Revasion</strong> is a minimalistic action arcade game with an energetic soundtrack. A challenging colorful bullet hell survival experience.<br><br>Rotate to dodge hazards and bounce back oncoming balls. Simple controls, hard to master.<br><br>A hybrid gameplay experience inspired by bullet hell and breakout classics.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Extra Game Modes</h2>Survive long enough and you'll unlock up to four bonus endless game modes for play.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Rebounce: Destroy all blocks and keep the ball on screen!<br></li><li>Evasion: Survive a never-ending bullet hell barrage!<br></li><li>Tension: You only have one block at a time. Keep the ball on screen!<br></li><li>Reaction: Ball changes colour every bounce, bounce it off the correct block!</li></ul>",
